description.narrative: In 2019, UNICEF Ecuador developed a new Communication Strategy, released its new website, and reached almost 14 million people through its social media channels and 12 million people by traditional media. Additionally, the CO launched a new campaign, called “Seamos Amigos” (“Let's be friends” in English), to promote empathy and prevent xenophobia inside schools; and developed partnerships with a regional editorial house, Santillana; a famous Ecuadorian writer, María Fernanda Heredia; and a local newspaper, Últimas Noticias to promote children`s rights | Status:On-track | As-of Date:25/01/2020
